  <brief_title>Use of Laser Speckle to Study Cutaneous Blood Flow at Exercise in Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <acronym>Speckle-move</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation Chez Des Sujets Sains d'Une Nouvelle Technique d'étude de la Microcirculation cutanée</official_title>
